11
00:00:41,601 --> 00:00:42,601
Mom...

12
00:00:42,921 --> 00:00:45,801
I told you we weren't soulmates.

13
00:00:46,721 --> 00:00:47,641
Alright, alright.

14
00:00:47,791 --> 00:00:49,001
Whatever you say.

15
00:00:50,431 --> 00:00:51,971
But I do like Win.

16
00:00:52,591 --> 00:00:54,701
She looks like a docile little girl.

17
00:00:57,771 --> 00:00:58,671
Mom,

18
00:00:59,041 --> 00:01:00,401
take good care of yourself.

19
00:01:01,571 --> 00:01:03,001
Watch your step

20
00:01:03,971 --> 00:01:06,771
and don't skip your meals.

21
00:01:08,081 --> 00:01:09,201
Alright.

22
00:01:09,651 --> 00:01:10,871
You too.

23
00:01:12,251 --> 00:01:14,271
Take care of those problems.

24
00:01:15,681 --> 00:01:17,941
So you two can break free from this karma.

25
00:01:20,071 --> 00:01:21,071
Sure, Mom.

26
00:01:21,621 --> 00:01:22,721
Thank you.

27
00:02:47,681 --> 00:02:49,348
It's gonna be fine, Win.

28
00:02:49,381 --> 00:02:51,311
We did our best.

29
