just because of that shoddy holy water?

108
00:10:42,351 --> 00:10:43,351
Try me.

109
00:11:04,868 --> 00:11:07,328
If you wanna change your mind...

110
00:11:07,528 --> 00:11:10,998
Do you think you can fight
the ghost of Jomkwan alone?

111
00:11:14,138 --> 00:11:15,688
Never step on those.

112
00:11:18,608 --> 00:11:21,478
A monk on pilgrimage wouldn't come
this deep into the woods to practice.

113
00:11:21,818 --> 00:11:28,148
